{"tid":649368,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam][Survival] Infestation: The New Z (2)","createTime":"2018-05-01T13:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T10:54:34.000Z","uid":39087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cae03396137b7a5f9a04a77459ae5862e6538391","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"官網: <a href=\"http://playnewz.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaynewz.com%2F&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=21b884e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://playnewz.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n Steam link: <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F555570%2F&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=125f6551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡介:<br />\n<br />\nInfestation: The New Z 係一隻一款殭屍生存大型多人開放世界遊戲，玩家同玩家之間嘅對戰係呢隻遊戲嘅重點，唔存在要周圍執食物去透爐BBQ嘅玩法，因為好難餓死。<br />\n<br />\nWar Z 係呢隻遊戲嘅前身，經過唔同版本嘅演替出 Infestation: The New Z。前者飽受穿牆自描外掛困擾，後者防外掛系統比較完善。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n課金問題:<br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲課金唔會令你勁啲，課金亦主要買 Premium account<br />\n<br />\nPremium account 主要有以下作用:<br />\n<br />\n1. 人物死左即刻復活唔洗比錢 or 等時間 （你亦可以等3分鐘 or 比 ＄15000 遊戲幤復活）<br />\n2. 每日送禮物（睇你運氣，通常垃圾）<br />\n3. 雙經雙錢<br />\n4. 原地復唔洗錢 冇P帳就15000$<br />\n<br />\n由於經常都有雙倍點數嘅活動，課金亦都相當抵<br />\n呢加黎講 40 HKD ＝ 4個月 Premium account<br />\n<br />\n一齊玩嘅有人課金亦有人冇課金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特點:<br />\n<br />\n1. Global Inventory<br />\n<br />\n係遊戲世界執完野（死會跌裝），可以登出伺服器，擺係大廳嘅Global Invetory （留返下次用）<br />\n<br />\n2. Skill Tree<br />\n<br />\n殺人 or 殺殭屍會攞到經驗值，經驗值可以用黎升級自己隻人物，例如冇咁易比殭屍察覺，瞄準器會再準啲之類。長玩嘅遲早都會升哂，但我地一班長玩嘅都未升哂，所以都算耐玩。<br />\n<br />\n3. Skin<br />\n<br />\nSkin 唔會有數值加成，係令呢隻遊戲耐玩度增加嘅其中一個因素。唔少 Skin 係會發哂光咁，一來型，二來招搖，變相會係地圖報自己位，對於有實力嘅人黎講，會無形中道出四字真言 : 夠做埋黎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣一齊玩歡迎入黎RC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRC: 26397891 （活躍玩家暫時3-4人）<br />\nTG:<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GanGVxJ6xftf1XQnqacjiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGanGVxJ6xftf1XQnqacjiw&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=3e6f19fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GanGVxJ6xftf1XQnqacjiw</a> (D 仆街掛機唔入TG GROUP)<br />\nSTEAM:<a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/id/nomoreha/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fid%2Fnomoreha%2Fhome&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=3dc41b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://steamcommunity.com/id/nomoreha/home</a><br />\nWhatsapp GROUP 都有 想入就 入TG 問我拎 (有1x人 係入面)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題都可以入黎問"},{"pid":"cbd88fb3f58e6cdb775ad00f8dfc8fcc9b1e6a36","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"新朋友注意事項:<br />\n<br />\n1. 盡量用近戰武器打殭屍，用槍會暴露自己位置<br />\n<br />\n2. 夜晚請帶夜視鏡<br />\n<br />\n3. 最好聯群結黨（2-3人）去執物資，安全啲<br />\n<br />\n4. 所有食物可以唔洗刻意執，肚餓只會扣血，唔會死<br />\n<br />\n5. 主要執步槍，e.g. M4A1, SIG556, L85, HONEY BADGER<br />\n<br />\n6. 唔等洗嘅步槍可以拆左排彈匣出黎，大部分彈匣都通用於其他步槍<br />\n<br />\n7. 敵人未發現你可以試下行近啲先殺，易爆頭，一兩粒足以收頭<br />\n<br />\n8. 善用藥物，盡量保持滿血，以免被收皮，建議藥物放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n9. 善用盾 (Riot Shield/Wood Shield) 擋子彈，保護自己，建議盾放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n10. 避免用錢復活角色同係商城買野，錢可儲起同其他玩家交易商城嘅野(平啲) or Skin<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手過來人有感:<br />\n<br />\n開始果陣比人虐待真係幾慘<br />\n雖然我呢加都係，但情況有好轉<br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲嘅真理就係要埋堆<br />\n三五成群出去冧友搶裝<br />\n唔小心奉獻左性命<br />\n就轉個頭返入去覆灼<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得玩到冇目標<br />\n短期黎講緊係要儲齊彈藥<br />\n同人開片至少都準備好頭盔呀，盔甲呀，槍啦大佬<br />\n長遠黎講我想虐待返其他人<br />\n<br />\n唔好灰心！堅持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔課金玩得唔得<br />\nA: 得。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 車點用？<br />\nA: 車只可以係 Beginner Server / Premium Server / Private Server 用，對住部車按實 F5 可以收返部車。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我得一個人，可以點玩？<br />\nA: 可以簡啲最少人嘅 Server，因為呢啲 Server 都係單人出團勝地，你得一個時人地都係得一個，自己安全執下野咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ: Beginner Server 可以玩幾耐？<br />\nA: 72 Hours<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點入 Official Server？<br />\nA: 係 Beginner Server 生存 1 Hour"},{"pid":"f2bebd2810f159933cb12b6d84ab71735dff69d3","tid":649368,"uid":176898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c0f02b1225ff8a45967cf9cfcfc3c015585f44bb","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2bebd2810f159933cb12b6d84ab71735dff69d3","tid":649368,"uid":176898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"LM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"可以入TG 搵我 呢個最快可以搵到我地"},{"pid":"e6695975fe2edb35d9c7679e5e83bf8615d0e1e6","tid":649368,"uid":176352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"巴打一齊玩 我哋都有人喎"},{"pid":"d43158f96d096a5c93bb004fb47a122928278c08","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bba04c27aec14f31f3cc0ddec0e58b8e28eefb6","tid":649368,"uid":108686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eef9070f07213851c0018948e1b78dfbd0dc8a3","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"6aa433794a7f92b1f3e1dd3e95f65cebba7083aa","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b22faa44bb30288c82e940069fb7961f03a9f04","tid":649368,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:58:53.000Z","m